import { Paper, Avatar, Typography } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

function SearchCards() {
    return (
        <Paper style={{width: "20%", height: "30%", position: "absolute"}}>
            <Avatar style={{marginLeft: "20%"}}>T</Avatar>
            <Typography align="left" variant="h5" style={{marginLeft: "10%"}} >Ed Revalo</Typography>
            <Typography align="left" variant="h6" style={{marginLeft: "10%"}}>Department</Typography>
            <Typography align="left" variant="subtitle1" style={{marginLeft: "10%"}}>Company</Typography>
            <Typography align="left" variant="subtitle2" style={{marginLeft: "10%"}}>Job Title</Typography>
        </Paper>
    )
}

export default SearchCards
